    {
      "id": "1ad4750c-f3ba-803a-ae5a-ce0c32afe918",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "To address this, the authors propose dynamic cognitive diagnosis, a model that is somewhat inspired by psychometrics and combines educational priors with DKT. The authors show that their model is not only more interpretable but proper selection of biases also boosts the performance of DKT models. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1ad4750c-f3ba-803a-ae5a-ce0c32afe918",
        "parent": {
